(177, 'Illustrator CC Advanced', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>Adobe Illustrator CC is an essential design tool for anyone who needs to express ideas visually in print, on the web, and in any other medium. In this course, which is a combination of Adobe Certified Instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice, you will learn the advanced techniques of working with Illustrator CC so that you can incorporate visual effects into your workflow.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nCreative professionals seeking the fastest, easiest and most comprehensive way to learn Illustrator CC.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X or Windows</li>\n	<li>Illustrator Fundamentals: An Introduction to Illustrator class or equivalent experience.</li>\n	<li>Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop class or equivalent experience is recommended.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\nCourse outline note: The curricula below comprise activities typically covered in a class at this skill level. The instructor may, at his/her discretion, adjust the lesson plan to meet the needs of the class.</p>', 100, 90, 12, 10, 1, 68, 2, 'days', '2020-07-11 13:12:12', '2020-10-18 03:55:25', 69, 'bf83798f14ba97a0e6a573aee0e5487d.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Illustrator-CC-Advanced', 'a5d9990de2158b85ffb738d4666d69f1', 'available', '5d9c8d891853069bfd84774d09c762a8.jpg', NULL, 2, NULL, '183f4d7c06b49f0ac8840bc5ba21a108.png'),
(178, 'Illustrator Fundamentals: An Introduction to Illustrator CC', '<p><strong>Course Details</strong></p>\n\n<p>Adobe Illustrator CC is an essential design tool for anyone who needs to express ideas visually in print, on the web, and in any other medium. In this three-day course, you will get a thorough overview of the interface, tools, and features of Illustrator CC. You will learn, step-by-step, the key techniques, as well as tips and tricks, for working in Illustrator CC. In this combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice led by Adobe certified instructors, you will learn the basics of working with Illustrator CC so that you can incorporate visual effects into your workflow.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nCreative professionals seeking the fastest, easiest and most comprehensive way to learn Illustrator CC.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of computers and basic Mac OS X or Windows skills</li>\n	<li>Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop class or equivalent experience is recommended</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Course outline note: </strong>The curricula below comprise activities typically covered in a class at this skill level. The instructor may, at his/her discretion, adjust the lesson plan to meet the needs of the class.</p>', 100, 90, 12, 10, 1, 139, 3, 'days', '2020-07-11 13:13:14', '2020-10-18 03:55:01', 69, 'c84126b7cbcc218393a2e32d820b80bf.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Illustrator-Fundamentals:-An-Introduction-to-Illustrator-CC', 'f062e50714a8ef0e5b5f49cdd482b5c2', 'available', 'ebfd6e38856ffe3cd8155b2de7257ea0.png', NULL, 1, NULL, '401961a9cf5fef1120cf98163f3da870.png'),
(179, 'Creating Section 508 Compliant Documents', '<p><strong>Course Details</strong></p>\n\n<p>This course is designed to become familiar with, and come into compliance with, the Federal Government&rsquo;s ADA Section 508 accessibility regulations. It covers both Adobe InDesign and Adobe Acrobat features to help meet those requirements. Students are expected to be familiar with InDesign and Acrobat already, as no time is allotted to review any basics of either application.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X or Windows</li>\n</ul>', 100, 90, 12, 10, 1, 26, 2, 'days', '2020-07-11 13:22:03', '2020-10-18 03:54:40', 70, '88762c6a880847761eaf004955821a1d.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Creating-Section-508-Compliant-Documents', 'f4db7f97489e3eff498427f23312b34d', 'available', '5c1e5bbfb41f491db782c8c330b80abb.png', NULL, 3, NULL, 'ba68b746b0dffa2e15da4cb022c89934.png'),
(180, 'InDesign CC Advanced', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>Adobe InDesign CC software speaks the language of professional designers, delivering unparalleled creative freedom, productivity,and precision for designing superbpages. It works seamlessly with Adobe Photoshop and Adobe Illustrator, providing a single integrated design environment that doesn&#39;t interrupt your creative process. This 2-day course provides a thorough overview of the interface, the tools, the features, and the production tips for page layout and design using InDesign. The course is an ideal<br />\ncombination of instructor-led demonstration and handson practice.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nCreative professionals seeking the fastest, easiest, most comprehensive way to learn InDesign CC.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X or Windows</li>\n	<li>InDesign Fundamentals: An Introduction to InDesign class or equivalent experience. Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop class or equivalent experience is recommended</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>​Course outline note:</strong> The curricula below comprise activities typically covered in a class at this skill level. The instructor may, at his/her discretion, adjust the lesson plan to meet the needs of the class.</p>', 100, 80, 12, 10, 1, 26, 2, 'days', '2020-07-11 13:23:09', '2020-10-18 03:54:12', 70, '4dc13a59b96ef8c9a1eca95a651a6b29.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'InDesign-CC-Advanced', '294db74af519d355a4af06826e59bf64', 'available', 'b1af2090399b8368607ce66339ecb23e.jpg', NULL, 2, NULL, '3d188266e9e17c3126689b43f2ad455d.png'),
(181, 'InDesign Fundamentals: An Introduction to InDesign CC', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>​​​​​​</strong>Adobe InDesign CC software speaks the language of professional designers, delivering unparalleled creative freedom, productivity,&nbsp;​and precision for designing&nbsp;superbpages. It works seamlessly with Adobe Photoshop and Adobe Illustrator, providing a single integrated design environment that doesn&#39;t interrupt your creative process. This 3-day course provides a thorough overview of the interface, the tools, the features, and the production tips for page layout and design using InDesign. The course is an ideal&nbsp;combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nProfessional designers who are new to InDesign.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X or Windows</li>\n	<li>Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop class or equivalent experience is recommended</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Course outline note:</strong> The curricula below comprise activities typically covered in a class at this skill level. The instructor may, at his/her discretion, adjust the lesson plan to meet the needs of the class.</p>', 100, 90, 12, 10, 1, 30, 3, 'days', '2020-07-11 13:24:02', '2020-10-18 03:53:24', 70, '03f8466b653d837486015519478dedd0.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'InDesign-Fundamentals:-An-Introduction-to-InDesign-CC', '3a7cce640c925544170dc04ac1cdfbfb', 'available', '7b0d7995e411a5251a467992df14247b.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, 'eb21a16a09e2f66a1f7d074ae8e798a4.png'),
(182, 'Muse Complete: An Overview to Muse CC', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>This 3-day course provides a thorough overview of the interface, the tools, the features, tricks, and tips for using Muse CC. The course is an ideal combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nDesigners who want to create dynamic websites without writing code.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X or Windows skills.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\nCourse outline note: The curricula below comprise activities typically covered in a class at this skill level. The instructor may, at his/her discretion, adjust the lesson plan to meet the needs of the class.</p>', 100, 90, 12, 13, 1, 13, 3, 'days', '2020-07-11 13:46:32', '2020-10-03 14:19:23', 71, '4fe7e09ff205ef64b599ef10daca953a.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Muse-Complete:-An-Overview-to-Muse-CC', 'cc03a16cc927158e195d299658a7669e', 'available', 'ee59ab4ad63f8da9e24fd1d849f07d2e.png', NULL, 0, '2020-10-03 14:19:23', 'a61c27be24a6d13fd6a349c044952b91.png'),
(183, 'Lightroom Fundamentals: An Introduction to Lightroom', '<p><strong>Course Details</strong></p>\n\n<p>Course Description Adobe Lightroom 5 softwares help you bring out the best in your photographs, whether you&#39;re perfecting one image, searching for ten,processing hundreds,or organizing thousands. This course is designed for novice photo editors to learn the basics of Adobe Photoshop Lightroom 5.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nPhotographers, designers or anyone else that wants a non-destructrive workflow to organizing and editing their photos.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong>&nbsp;<br />\nPractical working knowledge of computers and basic Mac OS X or Windows skills.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Course outline note:</strong> The curricula below comprise activities typically covered in a class at this skill level. The instructor may, at his/her discretion, adjust the lesson plan to meet the needs of the class.</p>', 100, 80, 12, 10, 1, 34, 2, 'days', '2020-07-12 14:38:10', '2020-10-18 14:50:54', 72, '49098cd7eddc7d00a4f2f70f43460bfd.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Lightroom-Fundamentals:-An-Introduction-to-Lightroom', '519e8c3c0da54e285aae07e02cd4444d', 'available', '3e5983ad2c92a468ac81387c6c9c6fb1.jpg', NULL, 3, NULL, 'd606836438ee56e0468f5ffec324425d.png'),
(184, 'Photoshop CC Advanced Web and Video', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>This 2-day course provides a thorough overview for experienced users who wish to further their effectiveness on Photoshop. This class is aimed at the<br />\nPhotoshop professional who needs to enhance their knowledge to work with web and video images more effectively. This course is an ideal combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nThose involved in any area of digital media, including desktop publishing, multimedia design, web design, digital video editing, and other disciplines for which Photoshop is the industry standardPhotographers and artists who work with photographs<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of computers and basic Mac OS X or Windows skills.</li>\n	<li>Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop class or equivalent experience is recommended.</li>\n</ul>', 100, 80, 12, 10, 0, 7, 2, 'days', '2020-07-12 14:39:21', '2020-10-16 01:50:29', 72, '40edde09b96f2d151e9ff89a298c7402.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Photoshop-CC-Advanced-Web-and-Video', '78581129f70f409c0da37099ae5f433f', 'available', 'da62aa46b0f64c82a31cf622c236bfe9.png', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(185, 'Photoshop CC Advanced: Print and Photography', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>This 2-day course provides a thorough overview for experienced users who wish to further their effectiveness on Photoshop CC. The course trains&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>photographers and designershow to catalogue their work as well as how to enhance their photographs. This course is an ideal combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nThose involved in any area of digital media, including desktop publishing, multimedia design, web design, digital video editing, and other disciplines for which Photoshop is the industry standard Photographers and artists who work with photographs<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of computers and basic Mac OS X or Windows skills</li>\n	<li>Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop class or equivalent experience is recommended</li>\n</ul>', 100, 80, 12, 10, 1, 33, 2, 'days', '2020-07-12 14:40:39', '2020-10-17 13:41:53', 72, 'bc38fab12953d21c513dd94a14783f4e.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Photoshop-CC-Advanced:-Print-and-Photography', '123d7bea8871a6d1b093002e9fd25f4b', 'available', '3b2700ad3bf2cb78b01754f437a40ca1.jpg', NULL, 2, NULL, '9a6a596f1d6d1805d62357b670dfba18.png'),
(186, 'Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop CC', '<p><strong>Course Details</strong></p>\n\n<p>Course Description This 3-day course provides a thorough overview of the interface, the tools, the features, tricks, and tips for using Photoshop CC. The course is an ideal combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nAdobe Photoshop has become an industry standard for so many different disciplines including desktop publishing, multimedia design, web design, digital video editing, and much more. Photoshop is often a prerequisite for many other software programs, and is the one program that everyone in every area of digital media should know.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of computers and basic Mac OS X or Windows skills</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Course outlines&nbsp;note: The curricula below comprise activities typically covered in a class at this skill level. The instructor may, at his/her discretion, adjust the lesson plan to meet the needs of the class.</p>', 100, 80, 12, 10, 1, 75, 3, 'days', '2020-07-12 14:43:19', '2020-10-18 03:52:32', 72, '478533b5a6105f92266cb108fe1c2d3d.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Photoshop-Fundamentals:-An-Introduction-to-Photoshop-CC', 'e6511fb3bd16274c791e0272a6ad9624', 'available', '303d8941ec5ee085e835fb3e5c7a70ff.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, 'c1a5df1a790a13279ab8125180557736.png'),
(187, 'Photoshop CC Advanced Web and Video', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>This 2-day course provides a thorough overview for experienced users who wish to further their effectiveness on Photoshop. This class is aimed at the<br />\nPhotoshop professional who needs to enhance their knowledge to work with web and video images more effectively. This course is an ideal combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nThose involved in any area of digital media, including desktop publishing, multimedia design, web design, digital video editing, and other disciplines for which Photoshop is the industry standardPhotographers and artists who work with photographs<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of computers and basic Mac OS X or Windows skills.</li>\n	<li>Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop class or equivalent experience is recommended.</li>\n</ul>', 100, 80, 12, 13, 1, 28, 2, 'days', '2020-07-12 14:45:42', '2020-10-18 04:08:28', 73, '5ef8c953f14a6039f20fb1c3e6dcd0d0.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Photoshop-CC-Advanced-Web-and-Video', '50e9d20cfc8201c7d1dbe5901050bd0d', 'available', '6df57427e508e7c19c84506c3efdaacd.jpg', NULL, 0, NULL, '9b448c1b3147426ecc207a2a755705d2.png'),
(188, 'Photoshop Fundamentals: An Introduction to Photoshop CC', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 100, 80, 12, 13, 0, 0, 3, 'days', '2020-07-12 14:48:39', '2020-10-16 01:49:47', 73, '466e3a8b1335c96c79d5e1fc4f573326.png', NULL, '', 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Photoshop-Fundamentals:-An-Introduction-to-Photoshop-CC', '3bc43a617f7b42d6d261e4822158b97c', 'available', 'ff638167eb64e3e729da69a85e1b02fd.png', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(189, 'Comprehensive Study of Premiere Pro CC', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>This is a 5 day class. The pace of the class is slower. The same content is covered in &#39;Introduction to Premiere Pro&#39; - a 3 day class. In this five-day course, you&#39;ll get a thorough overview of the interface, tools, features, and production flow for Premiere Pro CC. The course is an ideal combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice to introduce you to Adobe Premiere Pro software, a revolutionary 64-bit nonlinear video-editing application. You will learn powerful real-time video and audio editing tools that give you precise control over virtually every aspect of your production.<br />\n​<br />\n<strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nAnyone who&#39;d like to learn Adobe Premiere Pro CC<br />\nThose who plan to take the Adobe Certified Expert (ACE) exam<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Knowledge of Mac OS X and basic computer navigation</li>\n	<li>Basic knowledge of editing terminology is highly recommended</li>\n</ul>', 100, 80, 12, 14, 1, 27, 5, 'days', '2020-07-12 14:52:00', '2020-10-18 04:18:44', 74, '49dbf3e138d37ce930a3db857b16774c.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'acrobat course', 'Comprehensive-Study-of-Premiere-Pro-CC', 'def98bf0bb4a47faae6e466c68289ef3', 'available', '3f5d36aecef9bb7c2c901cda5d091823.jpg', NULL, 3, NULL, '49dbf3e138d37ce930a3db857b16774c.png'),
(190, 'Introduction to Premiere Pro CC', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>​In this three-day course, you&rsquo;ll get a thorough overview of the interface, tools, features, and production flow for Premiere Pro CC. The course is an ideal combination ofinstructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice to introduce you to Adobe Premiere Pro software, a revolutionary 64-bit nonlinear video-editing application. You will learn powerful real-time video and audio editing tools that give you precise control over virtually every aspect of your production.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nAnyone who&#39;d like to learn Adobe Premiere Pro CC Those that plan to take the Adobe Certfied Expert (ACE) exam</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X or Windows</li>\n	<li>​Basic knowledge of editing terminology is highly recommended</li>\n</ul>', 100, 80, 12, 14, 1, 59, 3, 'days', '2020-07-12 15:07:53', '2020-10-23 10:12:44', 74, 'a91d04863c9f61179823819b3c79f3c4.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Introduction-to-Premiere-Pro-CC', 'e0e9bb97dcb8d05bbf945e296f219f8c', 'available', '0cb203c3f3242bc6ce74534b82ddbe84.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, 'e9403289e1db58b79b8f286b27541a7a.png'),
(191, 'Premiere Pro CC Advanced', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>This 2-day course provides a thorough overview of the interface, tools, features, and production flow for using Premiere Pro. The course is an ideal combination of instructor-led demonstration and hands-on practice for getting to know this revolutionary nonlinear video-editing application. You will perform basic editing functions while familiarizing yourself with the user interface, and you will learn to use Premiere Pro&rsquo;s powerful real-time video and audio editing tools to give you precise control over virtually every aspect of your production.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Who Should Attend?</strong><br />\nProfessionals interested in creating videos using Adobe Premiere Pro and the applications that connect to it.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X or Windows</li>\n	<li>Introduction to Premiere Pro CC class or equivalent experience is recommended</li>\n</ul>', 100, 80, 12, 14, 1, 30, 2, 'days', '2020-07-12 15:08:52', '2020-10-23 10:12:31', 74, '9af6210290d36bbf1336677c6edb09c0.png', NULL, NULL, 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Premiere-Pro-CC-Advanced', '216e32f4ef6f229f999ea901783ca6d7', 'available', '5470d24067a99865d53ddba58e7492f2.jpg', NULL, 2, NULL, '9dc30df610668ee0d702b5e1bdecb1f5.png'),
(192, 'Premiere Pro for Experienced Editors', '<p><strong>Course Details&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>In this intermediate level class, students will go step-by-step through the entire editing process in Premiere Pro, from file creation all the way through output. Along the way they&rsquo;ll learn the ins-and-outs of file management, essential and intermediate editing techniques, color correction, audio mixing and repairing, titling and effects, and delivering their video onto tape, the web, and mobile devices. They&rsquo;ll learn to work within the Adobe ecosystem as well, getting up to speed on time saving tools such as Dynamic Link.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What You&#39;ll Learn</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Quickly organize your existing projects, or create new projects to use right away in Premiere Pro</li>\n	<li>Understand how to use Premiere Pro with other Adobe software</li>\n	<li>Edit your footage the way you like</li>\n	<li>Put your skills to work immediately</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Who Should Attend?</strong></p>\n\n<p>This class is designed for experienced editors who wish to learn Adobe Premiere Pro.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle; margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>This class is aimed at experienced editors. This is not a class for beginners</li>\n	<li>Practical working knowledge of Mac OS X</li>\n	<li>Avid, Apple or other NLE training or equivalent experience</li>\n</ul>', 100, 80, 12, 14, 1, 111, 2, 'days', '2020-07-12 15:09:25', '2020-10-18 04:17:21', 74, '5fa01059e2628c525dcfbcc02a6b58f3.png', NULL, 'https://vimeo.com/352302014', 'adobe', 'adobe', 'Premiere-Pro-for-Experienced-Editors', 'bb44141dfaca0cce13f96ddb94579207', 'available', 'f96c59c216f891069279dcc02c5a946e.jpg', NULL, 4, NULL, '8e3147efe650d7535aed89038f088c8d.png');
