ization</strong></p>\n\n			<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\n				<li>Learn how to read and write basic JSON. Also learn how to convert JSON to and from Swift types and into your own custom model objects</li>\n			</ul>\n\n			<p><strong>Working with the Web: Concurrency</strong></p>\n\n			<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\n				<li>Learn about the concurrency system in iOS and how to make sure code that updates the user interface is executed in the right place</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, '2020-09-17 19:51:11', '2020-10-18 01:39:11', NULL),
