(3, 'content', 'termcontent', '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Courseware Format Policy</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">E-reading device is not provided by Exceed Media. E-books material may not be available for all classes.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Discount Policy</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Discounts are valid on new class registrations only, and cannot be applied to prior booked, scheduled, or registered courses. Discounts must be mentioned at the time of registration.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Payment</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Payment must be received at least 15 business days prior to class start date. For anyone who registers within 15 days of the class start date, payment is due upon registration.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Cancellation policy of course/workshop:</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">If written notice is given 15 or more business days before the start of a class/workshop, the student/client may receive a full refund less registration administrative fee.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">If written notice is given less than 15 business days no rescheduling or refunds are permitted.</span></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:14px\">Student/Clients who commence a master class may not cancel and are responsible for the entire Master Class fee.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Exceed Media reserves the right to cancel classes with insufficient enrollment or in other circumstances. Exceed Media will endeavor to give as much advance notice as possible of any change to the schedule. Exceed Media shall not be responsible for any incidental or consequential loss arising whatsoever.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">All cancellations and registration changes must be received in writing. Please e-mail to media-training@exceed-media.com. Attendee substitutions may be made for any student/client without penalty or additional cost max one business day prior the class/workshop starting date.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Cancellation/Rescheduling Policy of exam:</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">If written notice is given 15 or more business days before the exam date, the student/client may reschedule or cancel without penalty.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">If&nbsp;rescheduling&nbsp;within 15 business days of the exam date, a $50 administrative fee will be charged.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">No Shows for a scheduled exam will result no refund fee.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">All cancellations and registration changes must be received in writing. Please e-mail to&nbsp;media-training@exceed-media.com.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Rescheduling Policy</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">If Student/client notice Is given 15 business daysor more before the class/workshopstarting date will be legible to reschedule class/workshopup to one time. Additional reschedules will not be allowed and will be consider as now show.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Exceed Media. reserves the right to reschedule a class if the number of participants drops below the minimum. In no event shall Exceed Media be liable for any incidental, indirect, special, or consequential damages, resulting from rescheduling or training.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>No Shows</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">If a student/client does not attend a scheduled class/workshop, there will be no refund or rescheduling permitted. Payment is forfeited.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Satisfaction Guarantee</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Exceed Media guarantees the quality of its training. If for any reason a student/client has not received the full benefit from a class/workshop, the student/client can audit the same class/workshop at no charge up to 3 months from course completion and from Exceed Media public schedule. The class can also be retaken online, if applicable. The request to audit must be made in writing within 10business days of the class completion.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Refund Policy</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Cancellations must be in writing in order to be eligible for any refund fees. if it is within constituted under our refund policy.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">All fees paid except registration fees will be refunded if the Client canceled before thirty (30) business days from the starting date of the class/workshops. However, refunds are not instant and will need processing of 15 business days.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Cancellation received after the thirtieth day prior to the class/workshops starting date will result in no refund of all fees.</span></p>', 1, NULL, '2020-05-21 04:13:17'),
